Third-party Advertisements

This application provides users the option of being served video advertisements from a third-party. 
We do not share any collected information with these third-party advertisers but they may collect 
and store their own information. Their privacy policies are linked below.

Unity Ads: https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy

Third-party Analytics

This application collects general usage data using Third-party Analytics services. 
This allows us to know things like how many users we have and what types of devices they use. 
The privacy policies of the Analytics services used are linked below.

Unity Analytics: https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
